Delete Your Account
Effective Date: January 1st, 2025
At
Easy Nex Tap NFC
, we respect your right to delete your account and associated personal data. You can request account removal through any of the following methods:
How to Request Account Deletion
From Inside the App:
Go to the
Settings
page in your account and select the
"Delete Account"
option.
Via Email:
Send a request to
sos@educacion.global
with a screenshot of the SMS you received from us.
Via WhatsApp:
Send us a message to the number you received the OTP code from the phone number linked to your account requesting deletion.
Data That Will Be Removed
Phone Number
Name
Avatar associated with your profile
Data That Will Not Be Removed
Information about NFC tags created using
Easy Nex Tap NFC
(this data remains for security and operational reasons).
If you have any concerns, feel free to contact us at
sos@educacion.global
.
Terms & Conditions
Effective Date: January 1st, 2025
Privacy Policy
At Educacion Global, Inc., we take your privacy seriously. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your personal information in compliance with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and industry standards for US Short Code Terms of Service, including the A2P 10DLC Campaign Approval Requirements.
1. Information We Collect
We collect and process personal data, including but not limited to:
Name
Email address
Contact information
Mobile phone number
IP address
Usage data
2. Use of Information
We use your personal data for various purposes, including providing and improving our services, responding to your inquiries, ensuring GDPR compliance, and managing our SMS and short code messaging programs. Your mobile information will not be shared with third parties or affiliates for marketing/promotional purposes.
3. Protection of Information
We take appropriate measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, disclosure,
                            alteration, or destruction. We use industry-standard security measures such as SSL encryption to protect your
                            data during transmission. We implement security measures to protect your data, but no method of transmission
                            over the internet is entirely secure. Please take necessary precautions.
4. Disclosure of Information
We do not share your personal information with third parties except as required by law or as necessary to
                            provide our services. We may share your information with our trusted partners who assist us in operating our
                            website or providing our services.
5. Cookies and Tracking
We use cookies and other similar technologies to collect information about your visit to our website. You may
                            disable cookies in your browser settings, but please note that some features of our website may not function
                            properly without cookies.
6. Your Rights
You have the right to access, rectify, or delete your personal information, as well as the right to object to or restrict its processing.
                            If you wish to exercise any of these rights, please contact us using the information below.
7. Updates to Privacy Policy
We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new
                            privacy policy on our website. You are advised to review this privacy policy periodically for any changes.
8. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy or our use of your personal information, please
                            contact us at sos [at] educacion.global
9. SMS and Short Code Terms of Service
By opting into our SMS or short code messaging program, you agree to receive recurring messages.
                                Message and data rates may apply. To cancel the SMS service at any time, text "STOP" to the short code.
                                If you need assistance, text "HELP" to the short code or contact us at sos [at] educacion.global.
Terms of Service
1. Acceptance of Terms
By accessing or using Easy Nex Tap, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service.
                                If you do not agree with these terms, please do not use the service.
2. Description of Service
Easy Nex Tap is a Software as a Service (SAAS) platform designed for seamless interaction with NFC tags. It enables users to scan and write data to NFC tags effortlessly..
